Move the `procustodibus.conf` and `procustodibus-setup.conf` files into this
directory, then restart the ProCustodibusAgentService. If the
ProCustodibusAgentService starts up successfully, the
`procustodibus-setup.conf` file will be deleted and replaced with a new
`procustodibus-credentials.conf` file.

See https://docs.procustodibus.com/guide/agents/windows/#run for details.
